{"tid":231374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蝗血蝗捐] 400佔港匪軍參加捐血","createTime":"2017-05-06T04:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T04:25:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01a1ba48ec5d7f2fca36ac977d9aa34980de39da","tid":231374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"佔港匪軍於九龍佐敦槍會山軍營駐香港部隊醫院，參與由支那紅十字會香港分會舉辦的捐血活動。今次是佔港匪軍第18次內部捐血活動，共400名匪軍參與。<br />\n<br />\n佔港匪軍陸軍下士陸淇表示，捐血可增進佔港匪軍與港蝗之間的情誼與瞭解，而且身為佔港匪軍，有義務參與公益活動。空軍下士紀威則稱，捐血可幫助別港蝗，故今年她再度參與。<br />\n<br />\n支那紅十字會香港分會輸血服務中心顧問醫生李卓廣稱，於香港紀律團隊中，佔港匪軍為人數最多的單日捐血團體。他又說，現時香港中央血庫血量偏低，希望每日有1100人捐血。"},{"pid":"b6489c8bb65ea8ec2928e93008ab643d1fbecf38","tid":231374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔港匪軍為人數最多的單日捐血團體。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寸鳩班黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9564cdd24da6dcc1c7730891d70e0b404ec741eb","tid":231374,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佔港匪軍為人數最多的單日捐血團體。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寸鳩班黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀蛇捐血唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c35c5d5f09574a95f7e3799900125e74e53db9","tid":231374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佔港匪軍為人數最多的單日捐血團體。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寸鳩班黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀蛇捐血唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辱黑警罪拉晒班匪軍"},{"pid":"eb09a2524c59c108e707f75a810ddab2a422c09c","tid":231374,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佔港匪軍為人數最多的單日捐血團體。</blockquote><b